(203, 203, 'Agent Deltchev Lvl2', '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>\r\n<npc xmlns="http://tempuri.org/NpcTemplate.xsd">\r\n	<objectInfo>\r\n		<id>203</id>\r\n		<name>Agent Deltchev</name>\r\n	</objectInfo>\r\n	<graphics>\r\n		<sprite>\r\n			<image id="0" name="deltchev.png"/>\r\n			<tileSize height="64" width="32"/>\r\n		</sprite>\r\n		<collisionArea>\r\n			<circle x="0" y="-10" radius="10"/>\r\n		</collisionArea>\r\n		<touchArea>\r\n			<circle x="0" y="-20" radius="20"/>\r\n		</touchArea>\r\n		<smallTalks></smallTalks>\r\n		<animation>\r\n			<anim id="0" desc="stand">\r\n				<script nr="0" src="7"/>\r\n				<script nr="1" src="4"/>\r\n				<script nr="2" src="10"/>\r\n				<script nr="3" src="1"/>\r\n			</anim>\r\n			<anim id="1" desc="walk">\r\n				<script nr="0" src=":6-8,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="1" src=":3-5,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="2" src=":9-11,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="3" src=":0-2,100"/>\r\n			</anim>\r\n		</animation>\r\n	</graphics>\r\n	\r\n		<statemachine>\r\n		<state id="0" name="waiting">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>*It seems like this is another 23 agent. You decide to talk to him later*</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="127" nextStateId="1"></scenarioCompletedEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="1" name="intro">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>\r\n         <p>Hey, pssst... You are the guy that helped Agent Blue in the first floor! I need to ask you something! Over here!</p>\r\n			</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n      <talk nextStateId="2"></talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="2" name="intro">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>\r\n        <p>I am Agent Deltchev. My friend told me that you helped him. I can tell you way more than he can. He is only a small fish in this aquarium. There is a lot going on here.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n			<question>Can I trust you?</question>\r\n			<answers>\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Yes of course you can trust me. I helped Agent Blue in the first floor and didn''t let him down. So what''s going on?"/>\r\n				<answer id="1" text="I''m not sure... I have to think about it. I don''t want to have problems here so I just come back to you later."/>\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="3"></answerEvent>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="20"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="20" name="Answer b">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>\r\n       <p>Okay, come back after you made up your mind.</p>\r\n			</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n      <talk nextStateId="5"></talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="3" name="answer a">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>\r\n        <p>I am glad to hear that. I can''t exactly tell you what''s going on here. We are an organization work- ing for the government. They are interested in the transactions this company is making with foreign investors. There are more people working on this but you have to keep it quiet.</p>\r\n        <p>Don''t talk to anybody about this! The spy agency has been after us for months. But right now I have a task for you. If you perform well I''ll tell you where you get more infor- mati