ome around for some assignments.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="20">\r\n\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="23" name="following of the player">\r\n      <text/>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>1</animId>\r\n      <movement>destination</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>1</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <reachDest nextStateId="24">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </reachDest>\r\n        <touch nextStateId="24">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </touch>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="24" name="talk to Player">\r\n      <text>Hey!</text>\r\n      <question>What are you doing in my office without my permission?</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="Hey Boss! I was waiting for you." correct=""/>\r\n        <answer id="1" text="Um, I was watering the plants." correct=""/>\r\n        <answer id="2" text="I have stolen your personal file." correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="25">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="25">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="2" nextStateId="251">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="25" name="Answer">\r\n      <text>Well, I don''t like it when people sneak around my office while I am not here.</text>\r\n      <question>Next time you talk to my secretary before you walk into my office without my permission.</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="Sorry, I didn''t know." correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="26">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="26" name="intro scenario 7">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>Okay, then I have another task for you, that you have to finish for me.</p>\r\n        <p>We lost a file on our system that contains all the ip-addresses of the network in this department. Your assignment is to find this .log file and to copy it to your home directory.</p>\r\n        <p>If you have done this, you should find out the ip-address of your own system and then name this log file like your ip-address.</p>\r\n        <p>It is really important that your file has the ending .log. If you need more information for this assign- ment you should look into your PDA under Wiki, where you can find all the information you need. Also you have to start the assignments in your PDA under Scenarios. There you will find information for your assignment too. Good Luck!</p>    \r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="27">\r\n          <triggers>\r\n            <skillTrigger skillId="7"/>\r\n          </triggers>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    \r\n    <state id="27" name="scenario 7 not finished">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>Do you need more information for your Task? You should look into your PDA under Wiki, where you can find all the information you need to finish it.</p>\r\n        <p>Also you have to start the assign- ments in your PDA under Scenarios. There you will find information for your assignment too.</p>\r\n        Good Luck!\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="129" nextStateId="28">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </scenarioCompletedEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    \r\n    <state id="28" name="scenario 7 finished">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>I saw that you finished your assignment.</p>\r\n        <p>That was really quick. I did not expect you to be finished by now.</p>\r\n        <p>But that is even better, because now you can already start with the next assignment.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="29">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="29" name="intro scenario 6">\r\n      <text>\r\n      	<p>This is your last task in this de- partment. You will learn something about file creation.</p>\r\n        <p>For more information about this assignment you should look into your PDA under Wiki, where you can find all the information you need to finish it. Also you have to start the assignments in your PDA under Scenarios.</p>\r\n	<p>After successful completion of your task you will be promoted and you will join Gina''s team from the Domain Management department.</p>\r\n        Congratulations!        \r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="30">\r\n          <triggers>\r\n            <skillTrigger skillId="6"/>\r\n          </triggers>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="30" name="scenario 6 not finished">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>For information about this assign- ment you should look into your PDA under Wiki, where you can find all the information you need to finish it. Also you have to start the assignments in your PDA under Scenarios.</p>\r\n        Good Luck!\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="139" nextStateId="31">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </scenarioCompletedEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="31" name="scenario 6 is finished">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>Wow, you''re an excellent worker. You have really proved that you''re ready for the next step.</p>\r\n        <p>You are hereby promoted. Well if you follow me I will introduce you to Gina. From now on you will be working for the Domain Manage- ment department.</p>\r\n        <p>Thank you very much for your excellent work. You have been a great addition to our team. I hope in the future you''ll be as successful as you were in our department.</p>\r\n        Thanks again.\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="32">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="32" name="walking to Gina">\r\n      <text>Just follow me!</text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>1</animId>\r\n      <movement>destination</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>7</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <reachDest nextStateId="33">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </reachDest>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="33" name="introducing the player to Gina">\r\n      <text>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n        <p>I hope you enjoy your new Job at the Domain Management depart- ment. I don''t have anything to do for you anymore.</p>\r\n        <p>So if you have any questions, you should go to Gina. She is your manager now and will give you the next assignments.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="34">\r\n          <triggers>\r\n            <trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="108"/>\r\n          </triggers>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="34" name="walking to office">\r\n      <text>I am going to my office!</text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>1</animId>\r\n      <movement>destination</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>1</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <reachDest nextStateId="35">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </reachDest>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="35" name="end state">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>I hope you enjoy your new job at the Domain Management depart- ment. I don''t have anything to do for you anymore.</p>\r\n        <p>So if you have any questions, you should go to Gina. She is your manager now and does have the assignments for you.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events/>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="100" name="introduction1">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>Hello, I''m the supervisor!</p>\r\n        <p>Well, I welcome you to our com- pany and we are all glad that you will support us from now on.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question>Do you need a tour through our department?</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="Yes" correct=""/>\r\n        <answer id="1" text="No" correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>true</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="1">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="12">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    \r\n    <state id="221" name="waiting">\r\n      <text>\r\n        It looks like you''re getting com-fortable with our department.\r\n        <br/>\r\n        Keep up the good work!\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <triggerEvent nextStateId="23">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </triggerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    \r\n    <state id="251" name="Answer">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>WHAAAAAAAAAT????!!!!</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question>No you didn''t!</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="Yes I did!" correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="252">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    \r\n    <state id="252" name="Answer">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>No you didn''t!</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question>...</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="YES I DID!!!!" correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="253">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    \r\n    <state id="253" name="Answer">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>NOOOOOO!!! YOU DID NOT!!!!</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question>...</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="Okay!" correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="26">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    \r\n  </statemachine>\r\n</npc>', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
INSERT INTO `adventure_npcs` (`id`, `npcid`, `name`, `xml_data`, `editor_data`, `created`, `modified`) VALUES 
(105, 105, 'Agent Blue', '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>\r\n\r\n<npc xmlns="http://tempuri.org/NpcTemplate.xsd">\r\n	<objectInfo>\r\n		<id>105</id>\r\n		<name>Agent Blue</name>\r\n	</objectInfo>\r\n	\r\n	<graphics>\r\n		\r\n		<sprite>\r\n			<image id="0" name="spy_agent.png"/>\r\n			<tileSize height="64" width="32"/>\r\n		</sprite>\r\n		\r\n		<collisionArea>\r\n			<circle x="0" y="-10" radius="10"/>\r\n		</collisionArea>\r\n		<touchArea>\r\n			<circle x="0" y="-20" radius="75"/>\r\n		</touchArea>\r\n		\r\n		<smallTalks></smallTalks>\r\n		\r\n		<animation>\r\n			<anim id="0" desc="stand">\r\n				<script nr="0" src="7"/>\r\n				<script nr="1" src="4"/>\r\n				<script nr="2" src="10"/>\r\n				<script nr="3" src="1"/>\r\n			</anim>\r\n			<anim id="1" desc="walk">\r\n				<script nr="0" src=":6-8,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="1" src=":3-5,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="2" src=":9-11,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="3" src=":0-2,100"/>\r\n			</anim>\r\n		</animation>\r\n		\r\n	</graphics>\r\n	\r\n	<statemachine>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="0" name="Player talks to agent blue before the secretary told the player to find out more about the agent">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>*This guy seems suspicious, but you decide to talk to him later.*</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="1"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for trigger from nerd after nerdtask2 -->\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="1" name="Agent Blue moves to the break room directly after the secretary told the player, that he might be suspicious.">\r\n			<animId>1</animId>\r\n			<movement>destination</movement>\r\n			<text>*This guy seems suspicious, but you decide to talk to him later.*</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>15</walkDest>\r\n			<events>			\r\n				<reachDest nextStateId="100">\r\n					<triggers>					\r\n						<trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="102"></trigger>\r\n						<!-- activate Secretary tasks -->\r\n					</triggers>\r\n				</reachDest>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="100" name="agent standing in the break room">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>*This guy seems suspicious, but you decide to talk to him later.*</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="2"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for trigger from secretary to go to break room -->\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="2" name="Waiting in the break room for to be triggered to talk to the player">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>!"§$"!§$"§$!"§</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<!-- <globalEvent globalEventId="190" nextStateId="3" /> -->\r\n				<!--wait for area trigger  replaced by touch event-->\r\n				<touch nextStateId="3"></touch>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="3" name="Player starts talking to Agent Blue after entered the break room.">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Hey...psst! Come over here...</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="31"></talk>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="31" name="Player starts talking to Agent Blue after entered the break room, 2">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>I am Agent Blue.</p> <p> I work here as a network super- visor and I am responsible if some- thing is wrong with the network connections on your terminal. Also I manage the email newsletter.</p></text>\r\n			<question>You''re the new guy?</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Yes, I just started working here. I finished a couple of assignments for the supervisor and the secre- tary earlier today. Now I am just looking around to find something to do." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="4"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="4" name="Player starts talking to Agent Blue after entered the break room.">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Well I am having a break.</text> \r\n			<question>...</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Do you like to work for this company?" />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="5"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="5" name="Player starts talking to Agent Blue after entered the break room, a">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>\r\n      <p>Well, its work. I rather would hang out on the beach and drink cocktails but it''s well paid, so I won''t complain too much. But there are certain things going on here that I don''t like.</p>\r\n      <p>Last week there was an attack on our network that only could have come from our own employees.</p>\r\n      </text> \r\n			<question>They accessed the personal files on our server.</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Really? Do you know who did this? Can I do something about it?" />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="6">\r\n					<triggers>					\r\n						<trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="102"></trigger>\r\n						<!-- trigger the secretary for next dialogues -->\r\n					</triggers>\r\n				</answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="6" name="Agent Blue gives the player his first task">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>\r\n      <p>We do not know who did this. Whoever did this changed the salary of one of our managers and changed the holiday plan of all other employees in this company.</p>\r\n      <p>I need you to change things back. You could help me with that.</p>      \r\n      </text> \r\n			<question>Are you interested?</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Yes, I have nothing else to do right now." />\r\n				<answer id="1" text="No, I am too busy right now. I might come back later." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<!-- player accepts -->\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="9"></answerEvent>\r\n				<!-- player declines -->\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="7"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="7" name="Agent Blue gives the player his first task, Player declines">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Okay, I am having a break right now so you can come back here if you decide that you want to help me with my assignment.</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="8" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="8" name="Player declined task in the first place and comes back">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>You''re back.</text> \r\n			<question>Have you decided to do my assignment?</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Yes, I want to do it. What is it about?" />\r\n				<answer id="1" text="No, thank you." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="19"></answerEvent>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="7"></answerEvent>\r\n\r\n\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="9" name="Agent Blue gives the player his first task, Player accepts">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>Awesome, I am glad that you will help because it''s a really tricky assignment. There are some chan- ges that have to be made on the personnel list of our department. The rest of the instructions you need can be found when you start the assignment in your PDA.</p><p> But you have to promise me that you don''t talk to anyone about this.</p>I can''t tell you why, but I will after you are finished with your task.</text> \r\n			<question>...</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Ok, I keep it quiet." />\r\n				<answer id="1" text="No, why should I keep things secret here? I am not doing this." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="10"></answerEvent>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="18"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="10" name="Player accepts, 2">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>Perfect!</p><p> As I already said. All the infor- mation you need for this you can find on your PDA. Also you can start the assignment in your PDA under "Scenarios". Be careful and make sure nobody can see you.</p> I talk to you when you are finished.</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="11">		\r\n					<triggers>\r\n						<!-- TODO: Skill fuer Scenario einfuegen -->\r\n						<skillTrigger skillId="5" />\r\n					</triggers>\r\n				</talk>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>	\r\n		\r\n		<state id="11" name="Waiting for scenario complete">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>After you finished your assign- ment I can tell you why this is a secret. I can''t tell you now.</p> If you need any more information about the assignment just look into your PDA under "Wiki". This should help.</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<!-- 130 vi/vim scenario -->\r\n				<scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="130" nextStateId="12" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="12" name="scenario completed">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>Okay. You finished this assign- ment and did very well. </p><p>I couldn''t tell you before why we have to keep this secret, because I needed to test your integrity. But it looks like you are a nice guy. Well, there are certain things in this company you don''t know about.</p><p>Since this company is developing software for the government there are always people spying on us. I am one of the agents working against these people.</p><p>You just helped us finding the security breaches in our network. Now we can resolve this problem. You can''t tell anybody about me. Otherwise they would get suspi- cious.</p></text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>			\r\n				<talk nextStateId="13" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="13" name="Agent gives task to steal supervisors file">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>Well, now you know too much to just walk back into your normal life. You have to work with us now. </p><p>I have another assignment for you. We need the personal file of the supervisor. It is lying on his desk.</p></text> \r\n			<question>Can you get it for us?</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Yes, I''ll get it." />\r\n				<answer id="1" text="No, I can''t do it." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="140">\r\n					<triggers>\r\n						<!-- TODO: richtige Trigger für Chef und File -->\r\n						<trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="107"></trigger>\r\n					</triggers>\r\n				</answerEvent>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="14"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="130" name="Agent gives task to steal supervisors file, alternate">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>We still need the personal file of the supervisor. It is lying on his desk.</text> \r\n			<question>Can you get it for us?</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Yes, I''ll get it." />\r\n				<answer id="1" text="No, I can''t do it." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="140">\r\n					<triggers>\r\n						<!-- TODO: richtige Trigger für Chef und File -->\r\n						<trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="107"></trigger>\r\n					</triggers>\r\n				</answerEvent>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="14"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="140" name="Answer a">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>I am waiting at your desk but hurry and be careful.</p>The supervisor doesn''t like people sneaking around in his office with- out his permission.</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="141" />\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="16"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for trigger from personal file -->\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="141" name="Agent Blue moves to the players desk">\r\n			<animId>1</animId>\r\n			<movement>destination</movement>\r\n			<text><p>I am waiting at your desk but hurry and be careful.</p>The supervisor doesn''t like people walking around in his office with- out his permission.</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>8</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<reachDest nextStateId="15"/>\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="16"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for trigger from personal file -->\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="14" name="Answer b">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Okay, but make sure you don''t tell anyone. <br/> We''re watching you. If you decide to do the task, I am waiting.</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="130" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="15" name="Agent waits for player to get the file">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>We need this file. Make sure you don''t get caught.<br/>Come back here as soon as you have the file.</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<!-- TODO: sicherstellen dass getriggert wird -->\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="16"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for trigger from personal file -->\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="16" name="Player got the file successfully">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Hey, I heard you got caught.<br/>Did you get the personal file at least?<br/>Did he find out what you were doing?</text> \r\n			<question>Did you tell him something?</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="I didn''t say anything. I was hiding the file underneath my t-shirt, so he couldn''t see it." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="17"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="17" name="Player got the file successfully 2">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>Well, don''t worry. </p><p>I leave you alone for now and let you do your work. We talk later.</p></text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="170"></talk>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="170" name="final state">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>I have nothing more to tell you. </p><p>You should talk to Agent Deltchev in Gina''s department. He will give you more assignments and also has more information about the orga- nization. All I can tell you is that it''s a really big thing.</p> Try to find out more.</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events></events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="18" name="player declines 2">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Okay, if you change your mind you can come back. I hope you enjoy your time here in this company.</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="8" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="19" name="Agent Blue gives the player his first task 2nd try">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>I need you to alter the XML file concerning the salaries as well as the holidays of our employees which was changed during the last attack.</text> \r\n			<question>If you finish this I tell you some more stories about this company.</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="Yes, I have nothing else to do right now." />\r\n				<answer id="1" text="No, I am too busy right now. I might come back later." />\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>true</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<!-- player accepts -->\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="9"></answerEvent>\r\n				<!-- player declines -->\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="7"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n	</statemachine>\r\n</npc>', 'DEBUG DATA EDITOR', '2008-07-08 09:39:13', '2008-07-08 09:39:19'),
(102, 102, 'Secretary', '<npc xmlns="http://tempuri.org/NpcTemplate.xsd">\r\n	<objectInfo>\r\n		<id>102</id>\r\n		<name>Secretary</name>\r\n	</objectInfo>\r\n	\r\n	<graphics>  \r\n		<sprite>\r\n			<image id="0" name="secretary.png"/>\r\n			<tileSize height="64" width="32"/>\r\n		</sprite>\r\n		<collisionArea>\r\n			<circle x="0" y="-10" radius="10"/>\r\n		</collisionArea>\r\n		<touchArea>\r\n			<circle x="0" y="-20" radius="30"/>\r\n		</touchArea>    \r\n		<smallTalks>\r\n			<talk>Steve is a bit busy at the moment, may I help you?</talk>\r\n			<talk>You are a real sweety! *twinkle*</talk>\r\n			<talk>Don''t you have any work to do?</talk>\r\n		</smallTalks>    \r\n		<animation>\r\n			<anim id="0" desc="stand">\r\n				<script nr="0" src="7"/>\r\n				<script nr="1" src="4"/>\r\n				<script nr="2" src="10"/>\r\n				<script nr="3" src="1"/>\r\n			</anim>\r\n			<anim id="1" desc="walk">\r\n				<script nr="0" src=":6-8,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="1" src=":3-5,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="2" src=":9-11,100"/>\r\n				<script nr="3" src=":0-2,100"/>\r\n			</anim>\r\n		</animation>    \r\n	</graphics>   \r\n	\r\n	<statemachine>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="0" name="The Player talks to the secretary before he gets introduced to her by the supervisor ">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>Hello, I am the secretary of the supervisor.</p><p>I can''t help you at the moment but later I might have some more information for you. I am just put- ting together some things for a major assignment.</p>If you are interested, you should come back later.</text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="1"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for supervisor to introduce her to player -->\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="1" name="The player talks to the secretary after he was sent by the supervisor for the second task">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>I finished creating a major assign- ment for this department.</p><p>It is really important and needs to be done very quickly. You seem to be the right person for this task.</p></text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="101">\r\n					<triggers>\r\n						<!-- Skill fuer Scenario 137 -->\r\n						<skillTrigger skillId="2" />\r\n					</triggers>\r\n				</talk>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="101" name="The player talks to the secretary after he was sent by the supervisor for the second task, answer Yes">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>The assignment is about the "ls" command. </p><p>You have to list the files of a specified directory. </p><p>For more information about this assignment you should look into your PDA under Wiki, where you can find all the information you need to finish it. Also you have to start the assignments in your PDA under "scenarios". There you will also find more information for your assignment.</p></text>\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="2" />\r\n				<!-- 137 linux basics II: ls basics -->\r\n				<scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="137" nextStateId="3" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="2" name="Player talks to the secretary without having the task finished yet">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>I am sorry but I am not so familiar with all this technical stuff.</p><p>If you need more help look into your PDA under "Wiki". There you can find more information about what you have to do in your assignment. Also you can start the assignment under "Scenarios" on your PDA.</p></text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<!-- Szenarionummer für linux basics II -->\r\n				<scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="137" nextStateId="3" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="3" name="Player talks to the secretary after he finished the task">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Oh...<p>I heard you did a good job. You might be a really good addition to our team. I am glad, because you seem really nice.</p><p>Get yourself a cup of coffee and then we see, if we find some more assignments for you.</p><p>By the way, if you need more help with all this Linux stuff you should talk to our nerd. He''s always sitting at his desk so you can''t miss him.</p></text> \r\n\r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="31">\r\n					<triggers>					\r\n						<trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="104"></trigger>\r\n						<!-- activate nerds tasks -->\r\n					</triggers>\r\n				</talk>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="31" name="Player talks to the secretary after she sent him to the nerd">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>If you need more help with all this Linux stuff you should talk to our nerd. He is always sitting at his desk so you can''t miss him.</p>We talk later, ok?</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="32"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for trigger from