oks a bit suspicious. I think he is planning something behind our back. But I don''t know what...</p><p>Well however, if you hear some- thing let me know.</p></text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<triggerEvent nextStateId="5"></triggerEvent>\r\n				<!--wait for trigger from agent blue -->\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="5" name="Player talks to the secretary and talked to the spy agent">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Do you know what''s going on with this guy in the kitchen?</text> \r\n			<question>Did he tell you something?</question>\r\n			<answers multipleChoice="false">\r\n				<answer id="0" text="No, we just introduced ourselves thats all. He didn''t say anything suspicious."/>\r\n			</answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="6"></answerEvent>\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="6" name="Player talks to the secretary and talked to the spy agent, answer a">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text>Well okay. <p>I have to do some paperwork for the supervisor. I call you as soon as I get some new assignments in.</p>So if you will excuse me for a second.</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events>\r\n				<talk nextStateId="7" />\r\n			</events>\r\n			<autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n		<state id="7" name="Player talks to the secretary after he told her that the spy agent is not suspicious">\r\n			<animId>0</animId>\r\n			<movement>stand</movement>\r\n			<text><p>Sorry honey, but I am pretty busy at the moment.</p><p>The supervisor might have some more to do for you. I call you as soon as I get some new assign- ments in.</p>I talk to you later okay?</text> \r\n			<question></question>\r\n			<answers></answers>\r\n			<visible>true</visible>\r\n			<walkable>false</walkable>\r\n			<walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n			<events></events>\r\n			<autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n		</state>\r\n		\r\n	</statemachine>\r\n	\r\n</npc>', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(104, 104, 'Nerd', '<npc>\r\n  <objectInfo>\r\n    <id>104</id>\r\n    <name>Nerd</name>\r\n  </objectInfo>\r\n  <graphics>\r\n    <animation>\r\n      <anim id="0" desc="stand">\r\n        <script nr="0" src="7"/>\r\n        <script nr="1" src="4"/>\r\n        <script nr="2" src="10"/>\r\n        <script nr="3" src="1"/>\r\n      </anim>\r\n      <anim id="1" desc="walk">\r\n        <script nr="0" src=":6-8,100"/>\r\n        <script nr="1" src=":3-5,100"/>\r\n        <script nr="2" src=":9-11,100"/>\r\n        <script nr="3" src=":0-2,100"/>\r\n      </anim>\r\n    </animation>\r\n    <sprite>\r\n      <image id="0" name="nerd.png"/>\r\n      <tileSize height="64" width="32"/>\r\n    </sprite>\r\n    <collisionArea>\r\n      <circle x="0" y="-10" radius="10"/>\r\n    </collisionArea>\r\n    <touchArea>\r\n      <circle x="0" y="-20" radius="30"/>\r\n    </touchArea>\r\n    <smallTalks/>\r\n  </graphics>\r\n  <statemachine>\r\n    <state id="0" name="Player talks to the nerd before he is sent to him by the secretary">\r\n      <text>*The guy who everyone just calls nerd is looking at you*</text>\r\n      <question>Hey buddy, what''s up?</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="Nothing, what''s up with you?" correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="11">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n        <triggerEvent nextStateId="1">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </triggerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="1" name="Player talks to the nerd after he was send to him by the secretary">\r\n      <text>\r\n        Hey... how are you?\r\n        <p>I''m pretty busy...</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question>What''s up?</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="The secretary told me that you can help me with some Linux basics. Do you have any assignments for me that I can learn more Linux basics with?" correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="2">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="2" name="Nerd gives player the first task">\r\n      <text>\r\n        Yes she was right.\r\n        <p>I have some learning assignments about Linux here that I can give you.</p>\r\n        <p>This assignment is for people who already finished the assignment about ls basics. I heard you finished it before.</p>\r\n        <p>In this assignment you will get additional knowledge about the usage of the "ls" command. For more information about the assign- ment please use your PDA.</p>\r\n        <p>If you have any questions about your task go into your PDA under "Wiki". There you will find a lot of useful information especially for your assignments. Assignments can also be started through your PDA under "Scenarios". Just click on the Scenario and then "Start".</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="3">\r\n          <triggers>\r\n            <skillTrigger skillId="3"/>\r\n          </triggers>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="3" name="Player talks to the nerd without having the first task finished yet">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>You have to finish the first task before I can give you any more help.</p>\r\n        <p>For more information about this assignment you should look into your PDA under "Wiki", where you can find all the information you need to finish it. Also you have to start the assignments in your PDA under "Scenarios". There you will also find more information for your assignment.</p>\r\n        Good Luck!\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="138" nextStateId="4">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </scenarioCompletedEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="4" name="Player talks to the nerd after he finished the first task">\r\n      <text>Okay, I hope you learned a bit more about Linux and the "ls" command.</text>\r\n      <question>Are you interested in more assignments?</question>\r\n      <answers multipleChoice="0">\r\n        <answer id="0" text="Yes, do you have another assignment for me?" correct=""/>\r\n        <answer id="1" text="No, thanks that''s enough for now. But I might come back later." correct=""/>\r\n      </answers>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="0" nextStateId="41">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n        <answerEvent answerId="1" nextStateId="42">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </answerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="6" name="Player talks to the nerd without having the second task finished">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>I am very busy right now.</p>\r\n        <p>Have a look at the black board (kitchen). There should be an assignment that suits you. It is about the find command. It should challenge you a bit more than the first assignment I gave you.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <scenarioCompletedEvent scenarioId="135" nextStateId="7">\r\n          <triggers>\r\n            <trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="105"/>\r\n            <trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="102"/>\r\n          </triggers>\r\n        </scenarioCompletedEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="7" name="Player talks to the nerd after he finished the second task">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>Hey, I am sorry but I don''t have anything else to do for you.</p>\r\n        <p>You have to excuse me now.</p>\r\n        I have to finish all my open tasks so I can go home to my family.\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>false</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events/>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="11" name="Player talks to the nerd before he is sent to him by the secretary, 2">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>Well I''m pretty busy as always.</p>\r\n        <p>I really think I have to do all the work in this company alone. Can you believe it?!</p>\r\n        <p>I just got five tasks that have to be done by tonight. How am I supposed to do this all by myself? Well I just have to hurry up.</p>\r\n        Now, if you will excuse me.\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="0">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </talk>\r\n        <triggerEvent nextStateId="1">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </triggerEvent>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="41" name="Player talks to the nerd after he finished the first task, a">\r\n      <text>\r\n        <p>Of course I have more assign- ments.</p>\r\n        <p>But as I am a little bit stressed out about my work at the moment you should go to the black board (kitchen). I put up a new assign- ment letter. Hope you enjoy it.</p>\r\n        <p>Remember: You''ll always find help in your PDA.</p>\r\n      </text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n\r\n\r\n        <talk nextStateId="6">\r\n          <triggers>\r\n            <trigger eventType="triggerEvent" machineId="121"/>\r\n          </triggers>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n    <state id="42" name="Player talks to the nerd after he finished the first task, b">\r\n      <text>Okay, I talk to you later.</text>\r\n      <question/>\r\n      <animId>0</animId>\r\n      <movement>stand</movement>\r\n      <walkDest>0</walkDest>\r\n      <visible>true</visible>\r\n      <autoTalk>true</autoTalk>\r\n      <walkable>false</walkable>\r\n      <events>\r\n        <talk nextStateId="4">\r\n          <triggers/>\r\n        </talk>\r\n      </events>\r\n    </state>\r\n  </statemachine>\r\n</npc>', '<editor>\r\n  <state id="0" x="0" y="0"/>\r\n  <state id="1" x="112" y="92"/>\r\n  <state id="2" x="150" y="150"/>\r\n  <state id="3" x="225" y="225"/>\r\n  <state id="4" x="300" y="300"/>\r\n  <state id="6" x="375" y="375"/>\r\n  <state id="7" x="450" y="450"/>\r\n  <state id="11" x="525" y="525"/>\r\n  <state id="41" x="600" y="600"/>\r\n  <state id="42" x="675" y="675"/>\r\n</editor>', '0000-00-00 00: